<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><i>Rashomon</i></h1>			<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
				<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>				<div id="contentSub"><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">  (Redirected from <a href="/w/index.php?title=Rashomon_(Kurosawa_film)&amp;redirect=no" class="mw-redirect" title="Rashomon (Kurosawa film)">Rashomon (Kurosawa film)</a>)</span></div>
				<div class="usermessage"><span id="mw-youhavenewmessages">You have <a href="/wiki/User_talk:68.133.21.33" title="User talk:68.133.21.33">a new message</a> (<a href="/w/index.php?title=User_talk:68.133.21.33&amp;diff=cur" title="User talk:68.133.21.33">last change</a>).</span></div><div id="jump-to-nav"></div>				<a class="mw-jump-link" href="#mw-head">Jump to navigation</a>
